title.rendered: …by any other name would smell as sweet

acf.description: My second painting inspired by a rose and using my pixel style of acrylic painting. I not only painted the canvas, but grew the rose as well.
I had a lot of fun with this painting, it helped to define my technique for future pixel paintings.
